date: UPS, FedEx Collaborate to Ship Pfizer-BioNTech COVID-19 Vaccines in US | LatestLYRival US companies UPS and FedEx are working side-by-side to ship the Pfizer-BioNTech Covid-19 vaccine, after it was approved for emergency use by the US Food and Drug Administration (FDA) on Friday....latestly.com
